_aChangeLog.text: Moved some crates in hallway slightly

_aLatestUpdates._sText: Added some decals to make the map look a bit better, and moved a couple of the crates that were in the bottom hallways, to allow for easier access through them.

_sText:
This is the same layout as the gg_wallrun_v1, but it has had textures added to it. Im not that great at texturizing just an fyi!

This is the first gun game map that I have made with hammer so it may have some issues, please let me know if it does and I will try and fix them. Also let me know if you like it (or hate it, lol). Any and all feedback or constructive criticism is greatly appreciated. Thanks!
